There is nothing of substance to this entire topic, so what's the point.  The PBE patch is there and mark/dash isn't going anywhere, it's done and your game mode is "ruined"

I don't know what goggles you're wearing, but I mostly see the ARAM Cry-hards being the ones plugging their ears and screaming about their "balance".  The board is flooded with complaint after complaint all from people who don't even play the core game, and think it's "boring" because it's not  cluster-fuck mini game like ARAM

Go hide in a bush and eat your Poro snacks dude

